Sentece: Similarly, there was 117% greater folate absorption fasting for Stuartnatal Plus (163 +/- 15 vs. 75 +/- 15 nmol, p < or = 0.001) and 57% greater absorption for Materna (207 +/- 21 vs. 132 +/- 13 nmol, p < or = 0.01).
Title: Vitamin B12 and folate bioavailability from two prenatal multivitamin/multimineral supplements.
Name: Cyanocobalamin
